1.7
log
@Don't try to revoque privileges if priv_init is called without
privileges. The parent process will be used for operations
that can't be pledged.
@
text
@/* $OpenBSD: privsep.c,v 1.6 2015/11/11 21:20:12 matthieu Exp $ */
